Exhibit 3-9: Market Penetration of Minivan Technologies
Exhibit 3-10 shows that sport utility buyers are highly receptive to 2X Hybrid, SIDI and Advanced Diesel technologies, which perform well from 2010 through 2030.
Flex alcohol and hybrids also show lower but still significant market potential.
Advanced Diesel and SIDI tend to dominate the pickup and large van market in 2010 with Advanced Diesel fading from importance in 2020 and later due to the rapidly growing popularity of the 2X Hybrid as indicated in Exhibit 3-11.
Pickup and large van SIDI holds prominence at about 20% market share through the entire analysis period, fading only slightly.
